description:
AKVIS Plugins Collection Multilingual for Photoshop

Software for processing graphics and digital images - retouching, painting, restoration. Retoucher-program for photo restoration and photo retouching. The program will help remove scratches, spots, dust, stains and other defects to remove unnecessary details, the text, to reconstruct missing parts of pictures, delay holey space and increase the ragged edge.

AKVIS Chameleon-program to create collages, realistic and fantastic.
Chameleon saves time and effort, so it does not require precise selection of objects automatically smooths the boundary and matches the color scheme &quot;insert&quot; to the background color.
AKVIS MultiBrish-brush set for image editing.
The program allows you to fix her chosen field of photography without much effort: to change the color saturation and sharpness, smudge object, tinted area, restore and conceal, remove unwanted objects and create an artistic collage.

AKVIS Enhancer-program for processing photos with increased image detail.
Enhancer improves the texture, emphasizes the details, pulling them out of the illuminated and shaded areas. The program supports HDR.

AKVIS Refocuspomogaet sharpen fuzzy, blurry, blurred images. With this program you can fix the whole image, or to edit only a specific area to focus on some details, like eyes, using the technique selective focus.

Program for coloring black and white photos and replacing colours on colour images.
Coloriageprost and understood as a child's colouring book, he turns the work into the game. A few dashes indicate sites for repainting. The program recognizes the borders, impose a specified colour, given the lighting, the play of shadows, folds in clothing.

Noise Buster - a program to suppress the digital noise.
The program removes digital camera noise matrix and the noise that appear when you scan a photograph and reduces graininess and eliminates non-uniform colour stain on the image, while maintaining detail and sharpness of the boundaries.

AKVIS Sketch-a tool for turning photos into the picture.
Sketch turns a photo into a work of art, converts the images into sketches in pencil, charcoal, watercolour, simulating manual work of this artist. With this program you can get not just black and white sketch, but a colour picture.

AKVIS Decoratorpozvolyaet to modify the surface of the object.
When applying the texture stored volume, shape, bends, folds, shadows of the original image. Using the Decorator can not just impose the texture, change it, but to load their textures, and simply change the colour of an object.

AKVIS LightShop adds light effects to the image.
With this program you can create any type and form of light, add a photo beams, halos, flashes, lightning, reflections on the objects, sunset or fireworks. LightShop decorate picture enliven landscape, change the time of day and weather.

AKVIS ArtSuite - a program for processing photos.
18 kinds of effects and frames, and more than 500 samples! ArtSuite can make an image, create an original greeting card, a holiday album, a poster or calendar, to turn a colour photo into a modern stylized black and white portrait, and even make color correction.

AKVIS SmartMask - Plugin for quick selection (cut) of the image.
SmartMaskpozvolyaet quickly and accurately allocate part of the picture or cut the figure of a man from a photo using relatively simple manipulation. The plugin is used to remove the background, creating collages.

Magnifierpozvolyaet resize images without losing quality.
You can not only reduce the image to put it on the Web or send to friends. The program allows you to receive the highest quality images from a small picture. Magnifier provides a manifold increase in the image without the artifacts and ghosting.

AKVIS ArtWork allows you to create a digital photo realistic painting, as if written by the artist. The program simulates an oil painting, imposes strokes so that the image looks like a work of art! It is possible to choose the type of canvas, add text to the design on the finished canvas.

AKVIS NatureArt - a collection of unique effects that simulate natural phenomena. The program allows you to add a photo rain, snow, lightning, sun and clouds change the weather, prevnesti a dramatic image, change the mood of the scene, a seascape or a picture of night sky.

